%% otel-traceparent — trace context propagation (offline Mermaid source for otel-traceparent.svg)
flowchart LR
  In["Inbound<br/>traceparent"]

  subgraph Trace["one trace id"]
    SvcSpan["Service span<br/>handler"]
    WorkerSpan["Worker span<br/>job"]
    SagaSpan["Saga span<br/>step"]
  end

  In --> SvcSpan
  SvcSpan -->|enqueue (propagated)| WorkerSpan
  WorkerSpan -->|continued| SagaSpan

  Otlp["OTLP collector"]
  SvcSpan -.->|export spans| Otlp
  WorkerSpan -.->|export spans| Otlp
  SagaSpan -.->|export spans| Otlp
